Defines software applications which are necessary to perform complete ITS service. Applications can be linked to components or sub systems.

Requirement Category definition
High Level: Has impacts and links to more then one stereotype or architecture element and is full filled by all of them together.
Low Level: Has impact and link one single stereotype or architecture element and is fully realized by it.
Specific high level R. - Safety: In terms of system operation.
Specific high level R. - Security: In terms of secure data and functionality.
